trans-unit.source: Provides the services for management of <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Tillhandahåller tjänster för hantering av <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] WorkflowQueuingService provides methods that you can use to manage the workflow queues associated with a workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]WorkflowQueuingService innehåller metoder som du kan använda för att hantera de arbetsflöde köer som är kopplade till en arbetsflödesinstans.

trans-unit.source: Creates a <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue"></xref> by using the specified name and transactional scope.

trans-unit.source: If transactional is `true`, the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue> is only visible inside the current transaction.
trans-unit.target: Om transaktionella `true`, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue>visas endast i den aktuella transaktionen.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue>

trans-unit.target: Innehåller de oanvända objekt i arbetsflödet köerna som är associerade med den här <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueuingService"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: When a workflow instance completes or terminates all of the unconsumed items in its workflow queues that are associated with this <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueuingService> are moved to the PendingMessagesProperty.
